      <description>&lt;p&gt;Source: &lt;a href=&#34;http://githa.koyil.org/index.php/githartha-sangraham/&#34;&gt;TW&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;SrI: SrImathE SatakOpAya nama: SrImathE rAmAnujAya nama: SrImath varavaramunayE nama:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://githa.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/githacharya-2.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;figure class=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;https://githa.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/githacharya-2-232x300.jpg&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;img src=&#34;https://githa.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/githacharya-2-232x300.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;githacharya-2&#34; title=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://githa.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/alavandhar-emperumanar.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;figure class=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;https://githa.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/alavandhar-emperumanar.jpg&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;img src=&#34;https://githa.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/alavandhar-emperumanar.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;alavandhar-emperumanar&#34; title=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://acharyas.koyil.org/index.php/alavandhar/&#34;&gt;yAmunAchArya&lt;/a&gt; – &lt;a href=&#34;http://acharyas.koyil.org/index.php/emperumanar/&#34;&gt;srI rAmAnuja&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://githa.koyil.org/index.php/githartha-sangraham-audio/&#34;&gt;Audio recording of all SlOkams&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;e-book – &lt;a href=&#34;https://onedrive.live.com/redir?resid=32ECDEC5E2737323!212&amp;amp;authkey=!AGPtc3-qqanz9Hc&amp;amp;ithint=file%2cpdf&#34;&gt;https://onedrive.live.com/redir?resid=32ECDEC5E2737323!212&amp;amp;authkey=!AGPtc3-qqanz9Hc&amp;amp;ithint=file%2cpdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;yath padhAmbhOruhadhyAna vidhvasthAsEsha kalmasha: |&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;*vasthuthAmupayA dhOham yAmunEyam namAmitham ||  *&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;listenhttpyourlistencomsarathythothathrichathusloki-thaniyan&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://yourlisten.com/sarathy.thothathri/chathusloki-thaniyan&#34;&gt;Listen&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I worship &lt;a href=&#34;http://acharyas.koyil.org/index.php/alavandhar/&#34;&gt;yAmunAchArya&lt;/a&gt; by whose mercy my defects have been removed and I have become an identifiable object, i.e., previously I was like asath (matter) and now I have realized that I am sath (soul) after meditating on the lotus feet of &lt;a href=&#34;http://acharyas.koyil.org/index.php/alavandhar/&#34;&gt;yAmunAchArya&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
